name: Kendu Inu
description: Kendu Inu is a meme project centered on community building and future utility development. Operating on the Base chain, Kendu Inu’s motto is simple: “We don’t play games. We work.” With a dedicated pack of loyal soldiers, Kendu Inu is driven by the collective effort to create long-lasting value, aiming to build a strong ecosystem that goes beyond just memes. Together, our goal is to forge a future of growth and prosperity.
